rows.name: Ask Charles about this place.[ST:wait ]

rows.name: Discuss[ST:wait ]

rows.name: Ask Charles if he's heard any interesting rumors.[ST:wait ]

rows.name: Ask Charles to tell you his experiences with the Ma-non.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_SEL0041
rows.name: Ask Charles if he's heard any interesting rumors.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Charles about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_SEL1031
rows.name: Ask Charles to tell you his experiences with the Nopon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_MSG0001
rows.name:
This is where people come to play.
And that is serious business, my friend![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_MSG0002
rows.name:
No matter how much they try to make New LA like an
Earth city, stress continues to build in the residents.
And this is where they come to release it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_MSG0003
rows.name:
Sadly, the only serious player here is Joy,
who kindly challenged me to a tennis match.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_MSG0004
rows.name:
It sure would be nice if more people would take
advantage of this. ...So? How about you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_MSG0008
rows.name:
If you travel northeast from New LA, you can get to the
continent known as Oblivia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_MSG0009
rows.name:
It's famous for its sheer cliffs, large waterfalls,
and mysterious ruins in the shape of a ring.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_MSG0010
rows.name: And they're all fantastic climbing spots![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_MSG0011
rows.name:
If it weren't for the aggressive indigens,
I'd be over there climbing around right now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_MSG0020
rows.name: The Ma-non seem surprisingly interested in tennis.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_MSG0021
rows.name:
But they have a...unique way of approaching the game.
I taught them the proper way to play, but they said
they don't like to be bound by rules.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_MSG0022
rows.name:
That's fine. I guess. As long as they're having...fun...
N-no, I...I can't let myself get stressed about this...
Must...learn...to accept them...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_MSG0023
rows.name:
Because Joy accepts them, and she's the one who
invited me here to play...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_MSG0027
rows.name:
I'm sure you know that if you travel northwest from
New LA, you'll reach the continent of Noctilum.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_MSG0028
rows.name:
A while ago, I asked a Reclaimer friend of mine to
show me around the region while he was on a mission.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_MSG0029
rows.name: It's a perfect spot for nature-focused activities.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_MSG0030
rows.name:
It would be a dream destination if you didn't have to
deal with being attacked by indigens.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_MSG1001
rows.name:
The Orphe have followed the Ma-non's lead,
and are now showing an interest in tennis.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_MSG1002
rows.name:
I taught Ton'barac the rules, and he seemed to
memorize them immediately. I haven't won a game
against him since![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_MSG1003
rows.name:
When I asked him how he does it, he said that
"the rules and theory of tennis are woven into the
weave of the net."[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_MSG1004
rows.name: It was...interesting. What else can I say?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_MSG1008
rows.name:
Now the Nopon are acquiring an interest in tennis,
but...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_MSG1009
rows.name:
Well, even after I kindly taught them the rules,
they decided it was more fun to just hit the ball
as far as they possibly could.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_MSG1010
rows.name:
And soon enough, they got a home run.
...With one of our last remaining balls.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_MSG1011
rows.name: But I...can't let myself...get stressed about this...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015901_MSG1012
rows.name:
Because Joy accepts them, and she's the one who
invited me here to play...[ST:wait ]
